NarNarrative:
Inspiration

,

The natural world continues to inspire people to create objects for their protection. Animal defences sich as horns have inspired items such as swords, copying their curved shape and sharp tip. Can you see how the springbok horns are sword are similar?

,

Springbok Horns

,

The horns of this animal curve inwards with sharp tips. These act as effective defence weapons when male spingboks lock horns during fights.

,

Sword

,

The curved and very sharp edges of this weapon make it a scary and dangerous item. Like the Springbok horns, this shape was good at locking with other swords and was important in defence too.
